               <code codeSystem="2.16.840.1.113883.6.1" code="34069-5" displayName="HOW SUPPLIED SECTION"/>
               <title> HOW SUPPLIED</title>
               <text>
                  <paragraph>5 mL sterile solution is packaged in a 5 mL white plastic DROP-TAINER* bottle with a plastic dispensing plug and white plastic closure (NDC 21695-204-05) containing tobramycin 0.3% (3 mg/mL).</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>
                     <content styleCode="bold">Storage: </content>Store at 2° - 25°C (36° - 77°F).</paragraph>
